original: Fahlcrantz, Johan Alfred Christian, landssekreterare, Vänersborg, f. 14/ ll/9’8 i Nyköping av landssekr. Wilhelm F. o. Gerda Berggren. ■— Stud:-ex. i Nyköp. 17, jur. kand. i Upps. 22. Tingstjg. i Västerbergslags doms. 23-25, e. länsnot. i Älvsb. 1. 26, länsnot. där 33, länsassessor i Södermani. 1. 36, tf. landssekr. i Älvsb. 1. 44, landssekr. där sed. 45.
translated: Fahlcrantz, Johan Alfred Christian, county secretary, Vänersborg, born on November 14th, 1898 in Nyköping to county secretary Wilhelm F. and Gerda Berggren. He passed his studentexamen (university matriculation) in Nyköping in 1917 and earned a law degree from Uppsala University in 1922. He worked as a court clerk in Västerbergslags district court from 1923-1925, assistant district notary in Älvsborg from 1926, district notary there in 1933, county assessor in Södermanland in 1936, acting county secretary in Älvsborg in 1944, and county secretary there from 1945.
